vulnerability_findings.name: pragma
vulnerability_findings.message:
Different versions of Solidity is used in IBasketManager.sol:
	- Version used: ['ABIEncoderV2', '^0.5.7']
	- IBasketManager.sol#3 declares pragma solidity^0.5.7
	- IBasketManager.sol#54 declares pragma solidity^0.5.7
	- IBasketManager.sol#55 declares pragma experimentalABIEncoderV2

vulnerability_findings.name: solc-version
vulnerability_findings.message:
Detected issues with version pragma in IBasketManager.sol:
	- pragma solidity^0.5.7 (IBasketManager.sol#3): it allows old versions
	- pragma solidity^0.5.7 (IBasketManager.sol#54): it allows old versions

vulnerability_findings.name: SOLIDITY_SHOULD_RETURN_STRUCT
vulnerability_findings.vulnerability_code: function getBassets() external view returns (Basset[] memory bAssets, uint256 len);
